OL,3,CSon's trainers left 'pattern' on mum's
OL,4,Cface as he stamped on her head
OL,6,FA court heard a man from Bury stamped
OL,7,Fon his mother's face so hard, the sole
OL,8,Fof his trainers left a distinctive
OL,9,Fpattern on her face.
OL,11,FStephen Ball, 32, attacked his mother
OL,12,FSuzanne Galvin, 55, at their home in
OL,13,FBury on 16 September 2023.
OL,15,FHe now faces life in prison after
OL,16,Fbeing found guilty of her murder.
