OL,3,CSon's trainers left 'pattern' on mum's
OL,4,Cface as he stamped on her head
OL,6,FSuzanne was found with extensive
OL,7,Fbruising to her body, including
OL,8,F"patterning" to her face consistent
OL,9,Fwith the sole of Ball's trainers,
OL,10,FBolton Crown Court heard.
OL,12,FJurors heard that neighbours reported
OL,13,Fa disturbance shortly before 8pm on 16
OL,14,FSeptember 2023, at a flat on Pear
OL,15,FAvenue.
OL,17,FBall was heard shouting abuse and
OL,18,Fcalling "Mum, let me in".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
