OL,6,FAfter the attack, Ball called his
OL,7,Fgrandmother, Mary Galvin, who lives in
OL,8,FIreland.
OL,10,FProsecuting, Gordon Cole KC, said: "He
OL,11,Fsaid he had come back to the flat to
OL,12,Ffind she was injured. He said he
OL,13,Fdidn't know if she had been attacked,
OL,14,Fbut said she was struggling to breathe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
