OL,4,Cface as he stamped on her head
OL,6,FSuzanne was found unresponsive on a
OL,7,Fmattress, and taken to Salford Royal
OL,8,FHospital, but died two days later.
OL,10,FA post-mortem found a blunt force head
OL,11,Finjury was the cause of her death.
OL,12,FIncluded in the report was reference
OL,13,Fto "patterned bruising" on her face
OL,14,Fwhich matched the pattern that was
OL,15,Ffound on Ball's ASICS trainers in his
OL,16,Fbedroom.
OL,18,F"This is consistent with stamping on
OL,19,Fher head or face," Mr Cole told jurors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
