OL,3,CSon's trainers left 'pattern' on mum's
OL,4,Cface as he stamped on her head
OL,6,FBall gave "conflicting" accounts to
OL,7,Fofficers when he was arrested. He was
OL,8,Fcharged with assault, before being
OL,9,Fcharged with murder following his
OL,10,Fmother's death.
OL,12,FThe court heard Ball and his mum had
OL,13,Fan "argumentative and aggressive"
OL,14,Frelationship as they both struggled
OL,15,Fwith addiction. Suzanne was seen with
OL,16,Ffacial injuries the day before her
OL,17,Fdeath, jurors heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
